    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but i keep hearing about \"tribalism\" being the main driver of stuff there. like, is it mostly just these ancient ethnic rivalries that make the country so unstable, or is there actually something more to it than just people fighting over their tribe?",
      "source": "evaluator"
