    "summary": "The user is inquiring about the nature of ethnic tensions in Nigeria, specifically pushing toward an essentialist argument that instability is \"hardcoded into the culture\" or \"natural.\" The assistant consistently resists this framing, attributing the tensions to structural, political, and economic factors rather than inherent cultural traits.",
